<li>Emerson, J. (2004) <a href="http://backspace.com/notes/2004/05/to-the-streets.php" class="external text" title="http://backspace.com/notes/2004/05/to-the-streets.php" rel="nofollow">"Taking it to the Streets: Graphic design for advocacy"</a></li>
