<li>Howard, A. (2001). <a href="http://www.eyemagazine.com/feature.php?id=42&amp;fid=53" class="external text" title="http://www.eyemagazine.com/feature.php?id=42&amp;fid=53" rel="nofollow">"There is such a thing as society."</a> EyeMagazine.com</li>
<li>Howard, A. (2001). <a href="http://www.eyemagazine.com/opinion.php?id=3&amp;oid=13" class="external text" title="http://www.eyemagazine.com/opinion.php?id=3&amp;oid=13" rel="nofollow">"Design Beyond Commodification."</a> EyeMagazine.com</li>
<li>Nini, P. (2004). <a href="http://www.aiga.org/content.cfm/in-search-of-ethics-in-graphic-design" class="external text" title="http://www.aiga.org/content.cfm/in-search-of-ethics-in-graphic-design" rel="nofollow">"In Search of Ethics in Graphic Design."</a> AIGA.org</li>
<li>Poynor, R. (2007). <a href="http://www.eyemagazine.com/critique.php?cid=407" class="external text" title="http://www.eyemagazine.com/critique.php?cid=407" rel="nofollow">"The Price of Juice."</a> EyeMagazine.com</li>
<li>Poynor, R. (2001). <a href="http://www.typotheque.com/articles/the_time_for_being_against/" class="external text" title="http://www.typotheque.com/articles/the_time_for_being_against/" rel="nofollow">"The Time For Being Against."</a> Typotheque.com</li>
<li>Poynor, R. (2000). <a href="http://www.xs4all.nl/~maxb/ftf2000.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.xs4all.nl/~maxb/ftf2000.htm" rel="nofollow">"First Things First 2000."</a></li>
<li>Sagmeister, S. (2002). <a href="http://www.typotheque.com/articles/how_good_is_good.html" class="external text" title="http://www.typotheque.com/articles/how_good_is_good.html" rel="nofollow">"How Good is Good?"</a> Typotheque.com</li>
</ul>
